snippet.title: Guardians Of Gaia: Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam: https://s.team/a/1718290

Guardians of Gaia is a team-based PvP Arena Brawler. Control the battleground using intuitive third person melee combat. Choose from a cast of powerful Guardians and join exhilarating battles.
